reviewText: One of the best SI swimsuit videos!

Great condition on both the DVD Disc and the DVD plastic case upon arrival. Makers of the VICTORIA's SERCRET Fashion Show should release their yearly TV show as an available DVD / Blu ray disc for Video buyers!
I've been collecting SI swimsuit editions for a while now, both magazine and special editions.  This was a perfect addition for my collection.

I got this because I'm a big fan of softball player  Jennie Finch. I've always had a crush on her and it was great  seeing her in a bikini on this DVD.The only downside of this DVD is that Jennie Finch was not on it more and the bikinis that Jennie Finch posed in could have been smaller. Not only is Jennie Finch the best softball player of all time but she is the hottest female athlete of all time too. I wish I could have been the photographer or someone that worked on  her photoshoot what lucky guys they were.
How can you go wrong with a DVD documenting some of the most beautiful supermodels In the world modeling bikinis or less. It's a great DVD, especially the body painting section ''

With the 04 Swimsuit Marisa Miller was the star & Again on this 05 edition she is blazing hot as always. I strongly recommend buying the 05 and 04 together, thats a great deal since I payed 20.00 for the 04 alone.

great models, great places, great suits...but too many blondes...

great dvd but i prefer the other ones.

Ana-Beatrice Barros is clearly the star as her body is impeccable and such a sculpted behind almost but not quite as perfect as that mystery girl see keyra Agustina Pandulce julieta or whatever she's called at Seekeyra dot com

You won't regret adding this DVD to your collection!!!
